SCHAEFER, Respondent, v. THORNTON, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 4, 1894.) Appeal from eighth district court. Action by Julia 0. Schaefer against William F. Thornton.

Argued before DALY, C. J., and BISCHOFF and PRYOR, JJ.

J. F. Higgins, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
